sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant QC as QueryClassifier
    participant PD as PersonaDetector
    participant HR as HybridRetriever
    participant CDB as ChromaDB
    participant BM as BM25 Index
    participant RRF as RRF Fusion
    participant PB as PromptBuilder
    participant LF as LLMFactory
    participant LLM as LLM Provider

    User->>UI: Types question and clicks Get Answer
    UI->>UI: Check cache (hash of query)
    UI->>QC: classify_query(question)
    QC-->>UI: QueryType (e.g. PROCEDURE)
    UI->>PD: detect_user_type(profile)
    PD-->>UI: UserType (e.g. EXPERT)
    UI->>PD: get_response_config(user_type, query_type)
    PD-->>UI: ResponseConfig (tables, length, style)
    UI->>HR: retrieve_with_metadata(question, top_k=5)
    HR->>CDB: similarity_search(question, k=10)
    CDB-->>HR: 10 semantic results
    HR->>BM: invoke(question)
    BM-->>HR: 10 lexical results
    HR->>RRF: fuse(semantic, lexical, top_n=5)
    RRF-->>HR: 5 RRFResult objects
    HR-->>UI: documents + timing + stats
    UI->>UI: deduplicate_documents()
    UI->>PB: build_adaptive_prompt(docs, query, config)
    PB-->>UI: Complete prompt string
    UI->>LF: LLMFactory.create(provider_config)
    LF-->>UI: LLMProvider instance
    UI->>LLM: generate(prompt, temperature=0)
    LLM-->>UI: Response text
    UI->>UI: Cache result
    UI-->>User: Display answer + sources + stats